  "original_title": "78 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b93\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "78-year-old retired president strangled to death - incident in Balangoda",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Balangoda police have said that a 78-year-old retired president and father of six, Aberathne, who belongs to Balangoda-Thutupola Thena area, has been strangled to death.",
        "While the murdered person has been living alone in the house for many years, a son went to the house this morning to provide food to his father. At that time, the father fell down with his neck cut and was immediately taken to Balangoda Aadar Hospital.",
        "However, the hospital authorities said that the person died before being taken to the hospital.",
        "In this situation, the dead body of the principal has been kept at the Balangoda Hospital for post-mortem examination and the Ratnapura Police Crime Prevention Unit and the officials of the Balangoda Police Station are conducting further investigations into the incident."
      ],
